<h4 id="field">Field</h4>
<p>A field is a set F which is closed under two operations + and $\times$</p>
<ol>
  <li>F is an abelian group under +</li>
  <li>F-{0} (The set F without additive identity 0) is an abelian group under
$\times$</li>
</ol>

